{"tid":1108381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭:逃犯條例修訂不設追溯期難接受","createTime":"2019-04-16T02:25:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T03:04:42.000Z","uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"27463e862a37ee355c08e22ecfbbbe2dafaf81d1","tid":1108381,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:25:32.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥出席行政會議前表示，為處理台灣殺人案，修訂《逃犯條例》存在迫切性，如立法會修例工作未能趕及，將會是大家不想見到的結果。<br />\n<br />\n她又稱，如未能與時間競賽，政府的修例工作亦不會停下，因為修例另一個原因是要堵塞現有法例漏洞，她希望立法會盡快完成審議工作。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥重申，保安局及律政司會繼續聽取意見，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>強調如涉及修例的根本，如要求修例不設追溯期，未必能夠接受</strong></span>。"},{"pid":"231a85af7fd31d5231c60824adfac653af40ce90","tid":1108381,"uid":211461,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:27:16.000Z","msg":"點解一定要秋後算賬<br />\n舞咁耐劍意在邊個"},{"pid":"345bef23c874417112de1495aa6d28787c20b165","tid":1108381,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:27:24.000Z","msg":"支持追到清朝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be8d13aa8736c3965e899c5c053dc195697394c8","tid":1108381,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:28:12.000Z","msg":"有尋秦記都無得走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006c344d513c06d77d937746388ace636facaa19","tid":1108381,"uid":211461,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"345bef23c874417112de1495aa6d28787c20b165","tid":1108381,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:27:24.000Z","msg":"支持追到清朝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:28:47.000Z","msg":"話就話要追台灣殺人條友<br />\n但人人都知呢隻野只係假target"},{"pid":"c314950f948012e46eff16b195937c852b563252","tid":1108381,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"231a85af7fd31d5231c60824adfac653af40ce90","tid":1108381,"uid":211461,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime